# Steps to reproduce

```csharp
using (var powershell = PowerShell.Create())
{
      // script setup snipped

      // This works and output is returned
      var results = powershell.Invoke();

      // This throws PlatformNotSupportedException on Linux (Ubuntu 18.04), but not on Windows
      if  (powershell.HadErrors)
      {
          // This, if tested in isolation also throws PlatformNotSupportedException 
          //  on Linux (Ubuntu 18.04), but not on Windows
          var errorRecord = powershell.Streams.Error.FirstOrDefault();
      }
}
```

# Expected behavior
No exception is thrown

# Actual behavior
Exception is thrown

# Environment data

Occurs with version 6.1.6 and version 7.0.0 of the System.Management.Automation nuget package
My project is compiled with NET Core 3.1 LTS

Complete implementation of host can be found here: https://github.com/fireflycons/PSDynamicParameters/blob/appveyor/tests/Firefly.PowerShell.DynamicParameters.Tests/TestCmdletHost.cs
